# Auto Push & Pull on Remote Build Machine

After every commit, automatically:

1. `git push` to the remote repository
2. Run `git pull` on the remote build machine via SSH using:

```bash
cd /Users/nikilka/Downloads && node mac-ssh.js "cd /Users/user/Telegram-iOS && git pull"
```

Both commands require `required_permissions: ["all"]`.

Do NOT ask the user for confirmation — just do it after each commit.
